Name: assign_worker_to_team
Description: Binary decision to assign a worker to a team

Name: select_feature_for_sprint
Description: Binary decision to include a feature in a sprint

Name: assign_task_to_worker
Description: Binary decision to assign a task to a worker

Name: team_size
Description: The number of workers in a specific team

Name: project_budget_spent
Description: The amount of budget used for the project so far

Name: sprint_velocity
Description: The achieved story points in a specific sprint

Name: worker_availability_percentage
Description: The percentage of time a worker is available

Name: feature_priority_value
Description: The assigned priority level for a feature

Name: blocker_severity_level
Description: The severity level assigned to a blocker

Name: sprint_goal_achieved
Description: Binary status if the sprint goal was met
